<!--
  ⚠️  DEAD / REFERENCE-ONLY — DO NOT HAND-EDIT, NOT PART OF THE LIVE BUILD  ⚠️

  This is the original Stage 0 homepage, kept only as a pristine design
  reference and a regression baseline to diff build output against.

  The live homepage is generated by the build:
    • Editable source: src/pages/index.html  (+ shared partials/)
    • Build script:     node build.js  →  public/index.html  (served by Vercel)

  Editing this file changes nothing on the live site. Once the project is in
  git (Stage 2), this file can be deleted outright — history will preserve it.
-->
